==Early life==
==Early life==
Teare was born 1 July 1911, and educated at [[King William's College]] on the [[Isle of Man]], and [[Gonville and Caius College, Cambridge]]. He trained at [[St George's, University of London|St George's Hospital, London]] from where he qualified in 1936.
